      "title": "How To Use",
      "properties": {},
      "widgets_values": [
        "Upload a video in `VHS_LoadVideo`.\n\nSet `force_rate` on the loader and `frame_rate` on `VHS_VideoCombine` to the same FPS.\n\nResolution presets:\n- 1280 x 720 = 720p\n- 1920 x 1080 = 1080p\n- 2560 x 1440 = 2K\n- 3840 x 2160 = 4K\n\nPasses:\n- `second_pass = false`, `third_pass = false` -> 1 pass\n- `second_pass = true`, `third_pass = false` -> 2 passes\n- `second_pass = true`, `third_pass = true` -> 3 passes\n\nIf VRAM or RAM usage is too high, disable extra passes or lower target resolution."
      ]
